webpackJsonp([0xf165229ef5c4],{944:function(e,t){e.exports={data:{wordpressPost:{title:"Laura Mercier&#8217;s Lightstruck Palette Is Here And It&#8217;s So Worth Buying",content:'<p>A handful of highlighting palettes have hit stores of late and while we have a few favourites, the team here at <strong>#TheBeautyInsider</strong> reckon this one by <a href="http://www.lauramerciertrimex.com.au/#">makeup artist turned mogul Laura Mercier</a> is definitely the pick of the bunch.</p>\n<img class="size-medium wp-image-2063 aligncenter" src="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/20202657/LM_Lightstruck-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" srcset="http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/20202657/LM_Lightstruck-300x225.jpg 300w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/20202657/LM_Lightstruck-768x575.jpg 768w, http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/20202657/LM_Lightstruck-1024x767.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" />\n<p>The real beauty of <a href="http://www.sephora.com/lightstruck-prismatic-glow-palette-P417251?skuId=1901826&amp;icid2=laura_mercier_whatsnew_carousel_us:p417251">Laura Mercier&#8217;s Lightstruck Palette</a> is that it contains five shades that can be blended together to create a personalised look, or alone for a genuinely radiant glow. And we swear to god &#8211; it&#8217;s made with some serious sci-fi S%$T because it reflects light in the most seriously clever way. Honestly.</p>\n<p>Laura herself recommends you use it in the following way:</p>\n<div class="page" title="Page 1">\n<div class="layoutArea">\n<div class="column">\n<p>• <strong>To begin</strong>, pickup AURORA with fingertips and apply a light application all over the face to immediately enhance complexion and provide a fresh warm appearance or a subtle base glow.</p>\n<p><strong>• Next</strong>, select favourite topper(s) to add dimension and shape on the high points of the face.</p>\n<p><strong>• If applying</strong> powder products next, set with Invisible Loose Setting Powder to gently fix makeup for all day wear.</p>\n<p><strong>• For more intensity</strong> on the cheeks, add additional AURORA onto the cheeks.</p>\n<p><strong>• TIP</strong>: On back of hand, mix AURORA or favourite topper to a crème cheek colour with fingertips and apply to cheeks.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n',better_featured_image:{source_url:"http://dcqiwphk5imn5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/20204836/Sephora-JPG.jpg"},categories:[{slug:"makeup",name:"Makeup"}]},site:{siteMetadata:{title:"The Beauty Insider"}}},pathContext:{id:"45ad6a32-e8f2-5928-b815-14f57c79d20b"}}}});
